

Test Case 1: User Registration

Preconditions:

The application is installed and accessible.
The user is not registered.
Test Steps:

Launch the application.
Click on the "Register" or "Sign Up" button.
Enter valid user information (name, email, phone number, etc.).
Set a strong password.
Click the "Register" button.
Verify that a confirmation message is displayed.
Check the user's email for a confirmation link.
Click the confirmation link in the email.
Verify that the user is redirected to the login page.

Test Case 2: User Login

Preconditions:

The user is registered.
Test Steps:

Launch the application.
Enter the registered email and password.
Click the "Login" button.
Verify that the user is successfully logged in and directed to the home screen.
